summary: with the idea of joxter being some sort of winter deity i imagine that he’s like. a reverse hibernator. he gets sleepy...
body: with the idea of joxter being some sort of winter deity i imagine that he’s like. a reverse hibernator. he gets sleepy throughout the winter and summer, but as it gets colder he begins to wake up more, thus being, like, a harbinger for winter, plus his personality gets “colder” while he’s much calmer and docile in the spring

summary: so ive seen a lot of Moomin Content on my dash lately and ive been considering getting into it and i just looked up the author...
body: so ive seen a lot of Moomin Content on my dash lately and ive been considering getting into it and i just looked up the author and just browsing over her life story made me start CRYING. like this woman put so much love into the world when she faced so much adversity,,, she just looked into the world with happiness in her heart and i just. ive never wanted to meet a dead person more. i want to make her tea and give her a hug and tell her that we will keep on putting her love out, no matter what. i havent even started watching/reading and im already getting EMOTIONAL this is gonna be a wild ride.
